==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Solemnly
<hw>Sol"emn*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a solemn
manner; with gravity; seriously; formally.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>There in deaf murmurs <qex>solemnly</qex> are wise.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I do <qex>solemnly</qex> assure the reader.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Solemnness</ent>⟦br⟧
